    "description": "欢迎加入《卡牌侦探》官方群！<br>qq群号：876115964<br><br>犯罪、刑侦、审讯。这些常见于悬疑剧、警匪片中的元素，是否能在游戏中呈现？<br>出于对相关知识的浓厚兴趣，制作组研究了大量犯罪心理学相关书籍，并咨询了相关从业人员，尽可能深入地了解这一学科。我们也将学习成果带到了《卡牌侦探》中，将其与剧情、玩法深度融合。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/ee3feec8326ba86018de4d7b33efd0c1.poster.avif?t=1740105470\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/ee3feec8326ba86018de4d7b33efd0c1.webm?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/ee3feec8326ba86018de4d7b33efd0c1.mp4?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在研究过程中，我们同时也在思考哪一种画风会更加贴合故事氛围。最终我们在写实漫画风格的基础上，通过阴影、线条、色调的丰富变化来展现整体氛围，预示剧情走向。这是我们在美术层面的一次全新尝试，希望大家能够喜欢！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/cdc45e002e068b73edb67f5e2ad9cea5.poster.avif?t=1740105470\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/cdc45e002e068b73edb67f5e2ad9cea5.webm?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/cdc45e002e068b73edb67f5e2ad9cea5.mp4?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2>玩家将扮演报社记者宫美雪，原本只是报道烂尾楼工地的事故演习，却在意外发生的坍塌事故中发现一具神秘尸体！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/e138b0742f9efbc2f293d9191931c3c9.poster.avif?t=1740105470\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/e138b0742f9efbc2f293d9191931c3c9.webm?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/e138b0742f9efbc2f293d9191931c3c9.mp4?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>面对证人们不同视角的主观陈述，为了查明真相，宫美雪竟找到身份神秘的酒馆老板学习刑侦学、心理学知识，并对证人们进行了询问。面对错综复杂的人物关系和接二连三的突发状况，宫美雪最终能否探明案件真相呢……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/63ea27ce8a87cfca8c5c3f8d80b5f34f.poster.avif?t=1740105470\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/63ea27ce8a87cfca8c5c3f8d80b5f34f.webm?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/63ea27ce8a87cfca8c5c3f8d80b5f34f.mp4?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >美术</h2>在写实漫画风格的基础上，通过阴影、色调的变化来展现故事氛围，预示剧情走向。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/7a799a2a3e8b7a6adee5b9570e3ec13b.poster.avif?t=1740105470\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/7a799a2a3e8b7a6adee5b9570e3ec13b.webm?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/7a799a2a3e8b7a6adee5b9570e3ec13b.mp4?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>人物动画方面，通过微表情的细致刻画，力图还原现实中被审讯对象的真实反应，将角色动作与表情的变化与玩法挂钩。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/76f96cd9ffff21c8c98ec65ea3318e6d.poster.avif?t=1740105470\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/76f96cd9ffff21c8c98ec65ea3318e6d.webm?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/76f96cd9ffff21c8c98ec65ea3318e6d.mp4?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法</h2>灵活构筑卡组，打出otk，一举击溃证人的心理防线！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/ae1108a983731ab003daedbcbb241350.poster.avif?t=1740105470\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/ae1108a983731ab003daedbcbb241350.webm?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/ae1108a983731ab003daedbcbb241350.mp4?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>细心了解故事，分析证言真伪，非传统卡牌玩法也能轻松制胜。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/b923ecebfe6485eb751b0123ad49c598.poster.avif?t=1740105470\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/b923ecebfe6485eb751b0123ad49c598.webm?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308670/extras/b923ecebfe6485eb751b0123ad49c598.mp4?t=1740105470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>各位侦探，准备好破案了吗？",
